{"type": "article", "id": 34781, "title": "看似朴素的木钟，想激励你不要拖延｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-11-22T23:05:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 35118, "name": "かみの工作所"}, {"id": 25154, "name": "Torafu Architects"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 103, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161122220728YX4kUSFse597M6no.jpeg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Flippr by Sharkk Labs</h3><p>为了减少人们在熨衣服上所花费的时间，美国设计团队 Sharkk Labs 对传统的熨衣板进行了改良，带来了这款声称能节约 80% 时间的熨衣板。Flippr 的奥秘在于它能够进行 360 度旋转，只要把衬衫套上去，抬起、翻转就能直接把两面给熨完了。而在熨裤子的时候，只要用尾部的夹子将裤管固定住即可。除此之外，它还附带了单独熨袖子和领子的小板子，进一步节省了时间。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/sharkklabs/flippr-the-ironing-board-that-saves-80-of-your-tim\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 99 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161122225638dho5HtAk7r2NRTiE.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161122225639CvlLMAtYUnmSX2Z1.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611222256409cIPgZiECdpuzlTV.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161122225638PTcgAeKXSw7qRi92.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Rubato Clock by Soezlar Technology</h3><p>当你看到由新加坡设计团队 Soezlar Technology 带来的 Rubato Clock 时，或许会觉得它只是一个朴素的木制时钟，实际上它隐藏了三种不同的运转模式，可以让时间走得忽快忽慢。这种听起来像是故障的设计其实是刻意用来帮助人们提高工作效率的：设计师们发现在追求产出的情况下，把时间加快会让人因为死线临近而集中精神；而在需要创意的时候，让时间放慢一点能够让灵感自由发挥。包括正常时间在内的三种模式均通过 Rubato 配套的应用进行调节，可以随时同步回正确的时间。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/466900800/rubato-clock-stretch-your-time\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 79 新加坡元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161122230419PFLyofpDMgdGkt6s.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161122222401z3ibZ8mYXpD9eA0l.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.451471\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611222224010IiPg4Cd8zaHUEyl.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161122222401c6ZkzHm2aKuFqJ30.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Ocean, Rainbow, Raindrop Air Vase by Torafu Architects</h3><p>谁规定花瓶一定得是硬的？这些能够根据需要自由改变形态的空气花瓶（air vase）是日本 <a href=\"http://www.torafu.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Torafu</a> 建筑设计事务所的作品，由制造商“纸的工作所”（<a href=\"http://www.kaminokousakujo.jp/index.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">かみの工作所</a>）利用轻薄的纸张打造而成。Torafu 曾经和一些艺术家合作推出过数款不同主题的器皿，最近又收到 TOTO 集团的委托，以“水”为元素打造了这套色彩斑澜的新系列<a href=\"http://torafu.com/works/airvase-oceanrainbowraindrop\" rel=\"nofollow\">“海洋、彩虹、雨滴”</a>。除了纤细的造型之外，花瓶底部漂亮的颜色变化同样相当吸睛。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611222223438AQixNv2X9pLUgac.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161122222344o6mDdWNcG5Tkwsjz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161122222343YEcf9T3UMezA4J5p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161122222343r8YJIpsMa4F0gbBO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161122222344NmUO9xfrBGq8CekR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Woodi by Hanna Särökaari &amp; Elina Ulvio</h3><p>芬兰设计师 <a href=\"http://www.hannasarokaari.fi/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hanna Särökaari</a> 和 <a href=\"http://www.elinaulvio.fi/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Elina Ulvio</a> 目前都就读于阿尔托艺术大学（Aalto University School of Arts）的家具设计系，最近她们合作设计了这款极简风的置物架 <a href=\"http://www.hannasarokaari.fi/designs/woodi/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Woodi</a>。架子的结构相当简单，依靠三点支撑，框架本身也能用作提手，携带起来非常方便。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161122225723aVQIDs48x1TNBAw3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161122225723kfZoe63nAVr8GL24.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.680247\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161122225723gJOl07MZU5jBz3dk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161122225724nEG5oHQ2PdSrB1z7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.919753\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Torqua by Pierre Villez</h3><p>法国设计学生 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/pierrevillaa05\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pierre Villez</a> 最近带来了一款名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/45128585/TORQUA-Flashlight\" rel=\"nofollow\">Torqua</a> 的概念手电筒，通过对光源的改造，让它能够提供更多的照明效果。除了精准地聚焦在某个位置之外，用户可以调整光源外的橡皮保护套改变照明的角度。铝制手柄末端附带的橡皮圈可以将手电筒悬挂起来，在户外当作吊灯使用。Villez 的构想是通过 USB 线进行充电，不过它的插头目前设计在手柄内部，需要将末端拆开才行。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161122222320KFp70cQUnkWyMfXo.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611222223200jkCQiMFaXKmB3Eg.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611222223198DztZkKLcH3q5Is6.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161122222324nDVNesTgk84Pf2AL.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161122222319YPCaKVxvtmsgW4QZ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161122222321JjSdV6OPGeZvwgkn.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Wallet Nail Scissors by Annabella Hevesi</h3><p>匈牙利设计学生 Annabella Hevesi 在一欧元市场里购入了一把指甲剪，剪刀统一的厚度启发她设计了一款让人能够将这件小工具带在身边的包装。这些金属卡片有为剪刀轮廓预留的空间，让人可以像收纳信用卡一样把它放在钱包里，同时也能保护刀头。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161122220925RwJ2P9AUex84YhkD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161122220927wvxEDLRuy4b2koVz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.511250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161122220925f0ES6CtGFsnJzoOu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.661875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161122220925jbpWAZNxoCdwDBqe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.615000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161122220927cDRUgnXsKCoq6O7l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.472500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}